<dl id="n15029i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n15" href="#n15029i">N15 (VI.D.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n15all.htm#n15029i"> 29(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> recension</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Ari&apos;s chief work was one entitled <i>Islendina-b&lsquo;</i> or &lsquo;Book of Icelanders,&rsquo; of which only a second and shorter <mark>recension</mark>, made by the author himself about 1130, has come down to us. <small> W. A. Craige, <a name="ICEL" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#ICEL"><cite title="source">The Icelandic Sagas</cite></a>, (1913) 24</small></blockquote> <mm class="note">Raphael transcription: <a name="c03202d" href="c03all.htm#c03202d">VI.C.03:202(d)</a>; <a name="c15205i" href="c15all.htm#c15205i">VI.C.15:205(i)</a> </mm></dd> </dd></dl>
